ori_caption: Figure 4: Comparison between a conditional generator and a generator that outputs an image/label pair. We expected the latter “dark knowledge” approach to outperform the conditional generator, but that does not seem to be the case. Because initialization and training of the dark knowledge variant were more sensitive, we believe a more rigorous tuning of the process could lead to a different result.
